Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,0:00:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.63,0:00:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Space.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.21,0:00:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reality.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's more than a linear path.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a prism of endless possibility,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}where a single choice{\i0}\N{\i1}can branch out into infinite realities,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}creating alternate worlds{\i0}\N{\i1}from the ones you know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am the Watcher.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am your guide{\i0}\N{\i1}through these vast new realities.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.13,0:01:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Follow me and ponder the question...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"What if?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.17,0:01:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We've seen this before,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a universe in the final days\Nof destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But this particular story...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This, this one breaks my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come. We got 90 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Start the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We got 30 seconds until their signals\Nreconnect with the hive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All clear down below.\NEighteen seconds, Clint. Clint?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not cool, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What? "Need a hand?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. I feel like\Nyou should know me by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Puns aren't really my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-We're getting rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Couple more seconds\Nand the Sentry signals would've
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:03:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,alerted the Ultron hive mind\Nto our location.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is... where, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Home, sweet home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what's left of it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really think\Nthe secret to taking down Ultron is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Russia, Hawkeye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Secrets were the national pastime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The end of the world began\Nwith one man's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a suit of armor around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.26,0:04:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} He saw a world of peace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the Mind Stone,{\i0}\N{\i1}Tony Stark created Ultron.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Ultron only saw one path to peace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The elimination of all life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} From puppet to puppet master,{\i0}\N{\i1}Ultron required one thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An organic body to call his own,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}one that fused the powers of man,{\i0}\N{\i1}machine, and mind into one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In your universe,{\i0}\N{\i1}the Avengers stole the Cradle{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and used it to create the hero, Vision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But in this universe, Ultron got his wish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:05:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the infinite power of the Mind Stone,{\i0}\N{\i1}Ultron began to lay waste to the planet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ultron's going{\i0}\N{\i1}after the nuclear codes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know if we can hold him off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to take out\Nthe satellite network.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't launch the nukes without them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't...\NYou don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I made you for peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,ULTRON{\i1}: {\i0}It's evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a primitive mind would fail\Nto see the distinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why you have to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-Emergency order 3-Alpha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Code Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're too late. He did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Laura...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the age of Ultron{\i0}\N{\i1}was only beginning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, I see everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There are worlds beyond my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Worlds that need... me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I'm going to bring about{\i0}\N{\i1}peace in our time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to every corner of the universe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Skynet,\NI've seen the killer robot movie
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and I gotta say,\NI really don't think it needs a sequel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You have spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It... is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At last.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The realization nearly broke the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,With his mission complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultron was now just a program\Nwithout a purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The victor without a war,\Nsentenced to spend all of eternity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who... Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Basking in the boundless{\i0}\N{\i1}silence of his universe,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ultron ascended to a previously{\i0}\N{\i1}unattainable level of consciousness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He became aware of another.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He became aware of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-I see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There are universes beyond my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have seen everything\Nthat has ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever will happen. Ever could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, what the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If a hunger like that were to be\Nunleashed upon the multiverse...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I will find you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I cannot imagine\Nthe horrors that might follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Even that machine is not\Nas invincible as it might think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There is still hope for this universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,One last hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the KGB archives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.88,0:11:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever seen\N{\i1}Raiders of the Lost Ark?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever seen that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Love that movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your countrymen never heard of PDFs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard copies are harder to steal,\Neasier to destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But code, code is slippery,\Nand it never dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.46,0:11:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think\Nwe learned that the hard way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.34,0:11:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where do we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just pick a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Clint? Clint?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this my color?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Don't try to make this fun, Nat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My will-to-live meter is flatlining, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The answer is right there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can show them. I can intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I could save the multiverse\Nand so many, many lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will find you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Look. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.17,0:12:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sit down. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up, come on. You're human.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep hope against the worst of odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Clint, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If we wanna take down Ultron,\Nwe need an AI that can combat his code.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yes, I know, but it's not here.\N-It's right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to break it to you, Nat,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the Death Star plans\Nare not in the main computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.34,0:13:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna find it. It just takes time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to avenge when we're 90?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.34,0:13:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're frustrated. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not frustrated. I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.67,0:13:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all lost so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm not sure there's\Nanything left worth fighting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already taken over\Nevery program on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. Every digital program.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that I have in mind\Nis a little more analog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Grab it. Grab it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-You did it.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just say you're gonna feel like\Na real jerk for almost quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, stop it! That...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You found it? That was my box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,An old HYDRA base in Siberia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Zola." What is that, an acronym?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a man. Or at least he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:13:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And he is gonna help us wipe out Ultron.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They really did it. There's still hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So many universes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So much chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They need to be silenced.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but it's my purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Scans show nothing alive.{\i0}\N{\i1}You sure this is the place?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Arnim Zola was a HYDRA scientist who\Ninfiltrated S.H.I.E.L.D. in its infancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Before he died in '72, he uploaded\Nhis brain to a series of data banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The one Rogers and I found\Nat Camp Lehigh was destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.38,0:14:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The other, HYDRA kept here to supervise\Nthe Russian Super Soldier program.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.67,0:15:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sounds like a real mensch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you wanna put all our eggs\Nin such a morally questionable basket?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The U.S. government once asked\Nthe same question about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take that as a yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Romanoff, Natalia Alianovna.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Barton, Clinton Francis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Francis"? Really?\NHow did I not know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.26,0:15:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a family name. After my mee-maw.\NDon't you worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mee-maw?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I imagine you have{\i0}\N{\i1}many questions, {\i0}Fräulein,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}about who and what and how I am.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really. I've actually met you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a copy of you. It's a long story.\NWe need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you work for...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And you know that I work for...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot has changed\Nsince you were last booted up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,HYDRA's dead. S.H.I.E.L.D.'s dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, pretty much\Neveryone else is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:16:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Courtesy of an AI called Ultron.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Und {\i1}I assume you want me to infiltrate{\i0}\N{\i1}his code and dismantle it from the inside?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a good number\Non S.H.I.E.L.D. the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why, pray tell, would you think that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}my strategic objectives{\i0}\N{\i1}would ever align with yours?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're the last surviving\NZola copy left on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've ruined a lot of laptops this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nein!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. Just ask S.H.I.E.L.D. IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right, all right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What exactly did you have in mind?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialing Avengers Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} Uh, hello?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'd like to order a pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? Who is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, do you guys offer\Na gluten-free crust?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Identifying your{\i0}\N{\i1}geo-positional coordinates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You havin' some fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, simple pleasures.\NI give us two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.34,0:16:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you might feel\Na little poke here, or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:17:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get how you work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Download commencing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And as for the mission parameters?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultron himself is currently off-world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, our only option is to upload you\Nvia a Sentry drone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We snag one, plug you in,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,90 seconds later,\Ngive the big guy a piece of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, he will not be{\i0}\N{\i1}the first genocidal megalomaniac{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have had to contend with, ja?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Torch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it'll hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Got 90 seconds to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Correction, 52 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have already initiated my signal blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it actually worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a precaution,\Nin case you wanna try anything funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your team-building instincts need work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Tell it to HR.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Time check.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hive connection in three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound promising.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Zola, better not be messing with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I assure you,\Nif I had a life to swear on, I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ultron hive mind\Nappears to be out of range.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That door is not gonna hold.\NWe gotta move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Move out, Clint. I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Clint!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Clint...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-I don't wanna fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Clint!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We should keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,More Sentries are likely on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why weren't you able\Nto connect to the hive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It is curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,According to my diagnostic,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the Sentries are rigged\Nfor interstellar communication.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.26,0:21:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever Ultron is,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,it does not appear to be\Nwithin the observable universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.67,0:21:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.\NThis should not be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.17,0:21:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but anything\Nis possible in a multiverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.34,0:22:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All those worlds,\Nall that suffering,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and you just watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.13,0:22:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I swore an oath. I cannot exert my will\Non the natural order of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the natural order of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.55,0:22:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I will bring peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.42,0:22:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It is my purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.34,0:22:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You lack the will to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.63,0:23:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot compute the power of my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Watcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I, Steven Grant Rogers,{\i0}\N{\i1}do solemnly swear...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.51,0:23:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire multiverse at your fingertips,\Nand you spent all your time up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. Isn't this more fun\Nthan just watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.92,0:23:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And to be honest,\Na lot less creepy on your part.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.88,0:24:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The boundaries of the multiverse\Nare irrelevant to beings like you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.71,0:24:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't evolve\Nby staying inside the lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.96,0:24:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, watch, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.21,0:24:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,From here, I can see everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.88,0:24:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can stop me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.01,0:25:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out of options.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.05,0:25:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing has left me no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.67,0:25:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.84,0:25:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Been living the dream alone\Nin a prison of my own making ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.88,0:25:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to break your oath?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.13,0:25:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.05,0:25:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Oh, yeah.\NI wanna hear you say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.67,0:25:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.21,0:25:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm about to say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.05,0:25:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.59,0:25:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your help.
